4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to prepare them for a career as a data scientist. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes per week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people.

The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and libraries like Pandas and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models.

The course emphasizes practical application and includes real-life case studies to prepare students for challenges they may encounter in their careers. Students will also learn to strategize and develop their own AI projects, covering the complete lifecycle from development to deployment and maintenance, with a focus on privacy and security.

Instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, who holds a PhD in Artificial Intelligence from Toronto University, Francesco Pugliese, a Computer Scientist with a PhD in Robotics & Artificial Intelligence, and Manuel Mena, a Senior Data Scientist with experience in Machine Learning and Business Intelligence.

Upon completion of the course, students will receive a recognized certificate. The course is taught in English or Spanish, depending on the student's preference.

For more information about the "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" course at 4Geeks Academy, visit their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning).

